{"tid":2365520,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「突發」眾院通過川普彈劾案 10位共和黨投了支持","createTime":"2021-01-13T23:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T08:11:19.000Z","uid":254371,"like":7,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"e58ef279d6c4af897bf396e99de6fe1c38125de4","tid":2365520,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T23:25:10.000Z","msg":"眾院彈劾決議案「H. Res. 24」有232人表決支持，其中十人為共和黨，包括眾院第三大共和黨領袖莉茲‧錢尼(Liz Cheney，懷俄明州)、紐約州眾議員卡特科(John Katko)、伊州眾議員金辛格(Adam Kinzinger)、華盛頓州眾議員布特勒(Jaime Herrera Beutler)和紐豪斯(Dan Newhouse)、密西根州眾議員阿普頓(Fred Upton)和梅耶(Peter Meijer)、俄亥俄州眾議員龔薩雷(Anthony Gonzalez)、南卡州眾議員萊斯(Tom Rice)、加州眾議員瓦拉道(David Valadao)，也使之成為美國歷史上最具兩黨共識的總統彈劾案；另有197人反對，還有5人棄票。"},{"pid":"53b00fa53d7a51be9dcd81ecc71c220076b414f6","tid":2365520,"uid":254371,"like":39,"dislike":7,"score":32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T23:26:13.000Z","msg":"原來咁多共和黨員都係共產黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40badcbc2164a2f7db58dd2999ba5b0fce015ca7","tid":2365520,"uid":313334,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"53b00fa53d7a51be9dcd81ecc71c220076b414f6","tid":2365520,"uid":254371,"like":39,"dislike":7,"score":32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T23:26:13.000Z","msg":"原來咁多共和黨員都係共產黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T23:26:54.000Z","msg":"全世界都係deep state"},{"pid":"22bd5a98b0ad3fefdf9003184257b94166d33b0f","tid":2365520,"uid":254371,"like":12,"dislike":7,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"40badcbc2164a2f7db58dd2999ba5b0fce015ca7","tid":2365520,"uid":313334,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"53b00fa53d7a51be9dcd81ecc71c220076b414f6","tid":2365520,"uid":254371,"like":39,"dislike":7,"score":32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T23:26:13.000Z","msg":"原來咁多共和黨員都係共產黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass